Daily World Readers Conference, Penn-Garden Hotel (31st Street and 7th Avenue), New York, New York. Participants include Manuel Vasquez (United Farm Workers), Susan Miller (Episcopal Peace Fellowship), Francis Gabow ( Daily World Chicago), Lucille Berrian (Welfare Rights), Jim Barreo (New Democratic Party of Alabama), Simon Gerson, Anton Krchmark, Ken Newcomb, Dennis Mora and Carl Winter. Photos by Bill Andrews.
